---
// Plain-SVG diagram for the local-first data flow. Inlined for zero JS,
// minimal request count, and good print/dark-mode contrast.
---

<figure
  class="card overflow-hidden p-4 sm:p-6"
  aria-label="Diagram: your AI agent talks to a local proxy on 127.0.0.1, which forwards to the LLM provider. An optional, opt-in dotted arrow sends pre-aggregated daily numbers to app.getbudi.dev."
>
  <svg
    role="img"
    aria-hidden="true"
    viewBox="0 0 720 220"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    class="h-auto w-full"
  >
    <defs>
      <marker
        id="arrowhead"
        markerWidth="10"
        markerHeight="10"
        refX="8"
        refY="5"
        orient="auto"
        markerUnits="strokeWidth"
      >
        <path d="M0,0 L0,10 L10,5 z" fill="currentColor"></path>
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <g
      font-family="ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace"
      font-size="13"
      fill="#e6e8ec"
    >
      <!-- Agent -->
      <g>
        <rect x="20" y="55" width="160" height="90" rx="12" fill="#11141a" stroke="#313846"></rect>
        <text x="100" y="90" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="600">your agent</text>
        <text x="100" y="112" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >claude · cursor</text
        >
        <text x="100" y="128" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >codex · copilot</text
        >
      </g>

      <!-- Local proxy -->
      <g>
        <rect x="265" y="40" width="190" height="120" rx="14" fill="#0f1f17" stroke="#22c55e"
        ></rect>
        <text x="360" y="72" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="700" fill="#22c55e"
          >budi proxy</text
        >
        <text x="360" y="94" text-anchor="middle" fill="#cbd5e1" font-size="11">127.0.0.1:9878</text
        >
        <text x="360" y="116" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >~6 MB Rust daemon</text
        >
        <text x="360" y="138" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >on your machine</text
        >
      </g>

      <!-- Provider -->
      <g>
        <rect x="540" y="55" width="160" height="90" rx="12" fill="#11141a" stroke="#313846"></rect>
        <text x="620" y="90" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="600"
          >LLM provider</text
        >
        <text x="620" y="112" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11"
          >anthropic · openai</text
        >
        <text x="620" y="128" text-anchor="middle" fill="#9aa3b2" font-size="11">github</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Arrows agent <-> proxy -->
      <g stroke="#9aa3b2" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" color="#9aa3b2">
        <line x1="180" y1="100" x2="262" y2="100" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></line>
      </g>
      <!-- Arrow proxy -> provider -->
      <g stroke="#9aa3b2" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" color="#9aa3b2">
        <line x1="455" y1="100" x2="538" y2="100" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></line>
      </g>

      <!-- Optional cloud arrow -->
      <g stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-dasharray="5 5" fill="none" color="#22c55e">
        <path d="M 360 160 C 360 195, 600 195, 620 195" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"></path>
      </g>
      <text x="490" y="212" text-anchor="middle" fill="#22c55e" font-size="11">
        opt-in: aggregates only → app.getbudi.dev
      </text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="sr-only">
    Your agent sends requests to a local proxy on 127.0.0.1:9878. The proxy forwards them to the
    upstream LLM provider. Optionally, the proxy can sync only pre-aggregated daily numbers to
    app.getbudi.dev.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
